=== 2018年国际足联世界杯 ===
==== 比利时和荷兰 ====
[[比利时]]国会议员{{link-en|阿兰·库图斯|Alain Courtois}}于2006年10月公开宣布[[比荷卢联盟]]的三个成员国：[[比利时]]、[[荷兰]]和[[卢森堡]]将共同申办2018年国际足联世界杯<ref name="Benelux">{{cite news |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=385813&cc=5901 |title=Benelux trio to apply to host 2018 World Cup |date=2006-10-16 |work=[[ESPN]] |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001045444/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=385813&cc=5901 |archive-date=2012-10-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年6月，这三个国家开始将申办世界杯一事提上日程<ref>{{cite news |url= http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=441938 |title= Benelux countries launch 2018 World Cup bid |work= ESPN |date= 2007-06-27 |accessdate= 2018-08-14 |language= en |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20121019131405/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=441938 |archive-date= 2012-10-19 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。随后，[[卢森堡]]宣布如果比荷卢联盟申办世界杯成功，该国将不会承办任何一场比赛，仅会主办一次{{link-en|国际足联大会|FIFA congress}}<ref>{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7095242.stm |work=BBC News |location=London |title= Benelux countries want World Cup |date= 2007-11-14 |accessdate=2018-08-14| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20071116110513/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7095242.stm| archivedate= 2007-11-16 |language=en | deadurl= no}}</ref>。

比利时和荷兰在2009年3月共同向[[国际足联]]正式提交了申办意愿<ref name=twelve>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7863406.stm|title=Twelve nations bid for World Cup|work=BBC News|place=London|date=2009-02-03|language=en|accessdate=2018-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204100348/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7863406.stm|archive-date=2009-02-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在此之前，[[比利时足球协会]]和[[皇家荷兰足球协会]]委派的代表团于2007年11月14日会见了国际足联时任主席[[塞普·布拉特]]，公开宣布了他们对共同申办世界杯的意愿<ref>{{cite web |url=http://fifa.com/worldfootball/releases/newsid=637931.html |title=Associations of Belgium and the Netherlands officially announce interest in submitting joint bid |date=2007-11-14 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071115095252/http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/releases/newsid%3D637931.html |archivedate=2007-11-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.sohu.com/20071115/n253263426.shtml |title=比利时荷兰有意联合申办2018世界杯 中国添劲敌 |publisher=[[搜狐|搜狐体育]] |language=zh-hans |accessdate=2018-08-14 |date=2007-11-15 |author=[[新华社]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080705180343/http://sports.sohu.com/20071115/n253263426.shtml |archive-date=2008-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年3月19日，该代表团还会见了时任[[欧足联]]主席[[米歇尔·普拉蒂尼]]，表达了他们的意愿<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.sporza.be/cm/sporza.be/voetbal/1.273169 |title= Ons dossier maakte indruk bij Platini |date= 2008-03-19 |work= sporza.be |language= nl |accessdate= 2018-08-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090327070252/http://www.sporza.be/cm/sporza.be/voetbal/1.273169 |archive-date= 2009-03-27 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

在提交申办主张时，比荷卢联盟的任何一个成员国都没有能同时容纳80000人的体育场<ref name="race20090317">{{cite news | title = The race to host World Cup 2018 and 2022 | first = Marc | last = Vesty | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7856716.stm#netherlandsbelgium | work = BBC Sport | location = London | date = 2009-03-17 | language = en | accessdate = 2018-08-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140517122500/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7856716.stm#netherlandsbelgium | archive-date = 2014-05-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。为解决该问题，鹿特丹市议会承诺在2009年3月完成对[[费耶诺德体育场]]的改造升级工程。2009年11月，比利时和荷兰提交了比赛场地安排计划。比利时的比赛将被安排在[[安特卫普]]、[[布吕赫]]、[[布鲁塞尔]]、[[沙勒罗瓦]]、[[亨克]]、[[根特]]和[[列日]]，荷兰的比赛将被安排在[[阿姆斯特丹]]、[[埃因霍温]]、[[恩斯赫德]]、[[海伦芬]]和[[鹿特丹]]<ref>{{cite news |work=Sporza.be  |location=Eindhoven  |agency=Belga  |url=http://www.sporza.be/cm/sporza/voetbal/wk/091109_speelsteden_WK  |language=nl |title=België krijgt zeven speelsteden op het WK 2018  |date=2009-11-09 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091111111437/http://www.sporza.be/cm/sporza/voetbal/wk/091109_speelsteden_WK  |archivedate=2009-11-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerfield24.com/world-cup-2018 |title=World Cup 2018 |date=2010-09 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en |publisher=Soccer Field |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814170106/http://www.soccerfield24.com/world-cup-2018 |archive-date=2018-08-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 英格兰 ====
2007年10月31日，[[英格兰足球总会]]正式对外宣布了关于申办2018年国际足联世界杯的意愿<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/international/article2779563.ece |title=FA confirms 2018 World Cup Bid |work=The Times |location=London |date=2007-10-31 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en |first=Rosemary |last=Bennett |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429084709/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/international/article2779563.ece |archive-date=2011-04-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年4月24日，英足总完成了长达63页的关于申办2018年世界杯的材料，其内容主要为发展世界足球的相关事项<ref>{{cite news |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/sow/news;_ylt=AjRl4htjIVNdu.daSX4XAgQmw7YF?slug=ap-england-2018worldcup&prov=ap&type=lgns|title= England plans its 2018 World Cup bid |work= [[Yahoo!]] |agency= Associated Press |date=2008-04-24 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en}}</ref>。2009年1月27日，英格兰正式向[[国际足联]]递交了申办材料<ref name=jointfail>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7832150.stm
|title=England submit 2018 World Cup bid |date=2009-01-27 |work=BBC Sport|location=London|accessdate=2018-08-14 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090119000948/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7832150.stm| archivedate=2009-01-19| deadurl= no}}</ref>。{{link-en|理查德·卡本|Richard Caborn}}在担任体育部长后，开始担起了申办世界杯的主要职责<ref>{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6249864.stm |title= Caborn to spearhead World Cup bid |work= BBC Sport |location= London |date= 2007-06-27 |accessdate= 2018-08-14 |language= en |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20070831061730/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6249864.stm |archive-date= 2007-08-31 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2008年10月24日，英足总成立了世界杯申办执行委员会，由[[男爵]]{{link-en|戴维·特里斯曼|David Triesman}}担任委员会主席<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thefa.com/TheFA/NewsFromTheFA/Postings/WorldCup2018_execboard.htm |archive-url=https://archive.is/20081015042409/http://www.thefa.com/TheFA/NewsFromTheFA/Postings/WorldCup2018_execboard.htm |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2008-10-15 |language=en |title= Board confirmed for 2018 |publisher=[[英格兰足球总会]] |date=2008-10-24 |accessdate=2018-08-14}}</ref>。然而，特里斯曼在2010年5月16日发表评论后辞职。他在评论中还建议，如果俄罗斯在[[2010年国际足联世界杯]]上贿赂裁判，西班牙应当考虑放弃申办<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.goal.com/en/news/1863/world-cup-2010/2010/05/16/1928333/geoff-thompson-replaces-lord-triesman-as-england-2018-bid |title= Geoff Thompson Replaces Lord Triesman As England 2018 Bid Chief |work= Goal.com |date= 2010-05-16 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-14 |first= Edward |last= Pearce| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100522021404/http://www.goal.com/en/news/1863/world-cup-2010/2010/05/16/1928333/geoff-thompson-replaces-lord-triesman-as-england-2018-bid| archivedate=2010-05-22| deadurl= no}}</ref>。

[[英国政府]]表示支持英格兰关于申办2018年世界杯的事项。2005年11月，时任[[财政大臣 (英国)|英国财政大臣]][[戈登·布朗]]和体育部长{{link-en|泰萨·乔威尔|Tessa Jowell}}首次宣布，他们将对申办世界杯的可能性进行调查<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.hm-treasury.gov.uk/newsroom_and_speeches/press/2005/press_96_05.cfm| title=Government launches work on 2018 bid| publisher=HM Treasury |date=2005-11-18 |language=en |accessdate=2007-10-29| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20071005103020/http://www.hm-treasury.gov.uk/newsroom_and_speeches/press/2005/press_96_05.cfm| archivedate=2007-10-05 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。同月，英足总传讯总监{{link-en|阿德里安·贝维因顿|Adrian Bevington}}公开称他支持这次申办，同时也提出了明确的建议<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.thefa.com/England/SeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2005/11/England_WorldCup2018.htm |archive-url= https://archive.is/20080720013206/http://www.thefa.com/England/SeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2005/11/England_WorldCup2018.htm |dead-url= yes |archive-date= 2008-07-20 |publisher=[[英格兰足球总会]] |title= World Cup bid latest |date= 2005-11-15 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en}}</ref>。戈登·布朗在2006年3月和5月还特意重申了他对支持申办世界杯的立场<ref name="fa66">{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/TheFA/Wembley/NewsandFeatures/2006/wembley_commemorate_66 |title=Heroes of '66 reunited |publisher=[[英格兰足球总会]] |accessdate=2018-08-14 |date=2006-03-21 |language=en |first=Mark |last=Whittle}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www2.goldmansachs.com/insight/research/reports/docs/WCB2006.pdf |title=The World Cup and Economics 2006 |publisher=Goldman Sachs |date=2006-05-03 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071029140706/http://www2.goldmansachs.com/insight/research/reports/docs/WCB2006.pdf |archivedate=2007-10-29 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。英国政府于2007年2月12日正式发布了申办世界杯的报告，明确了只有[[英格兰]]而非整个[[英国]]申办的地位<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.scotsman.com/news/politics/top-stories/chancellor-s-world-cup-fever-fails-to-grip-the-scots-1-681878 |last=Kirkup |first=James |title=Chancellor's World Cup fever fails to grip the Scots |work=The Scotsman |place=Edinburgh, UK |date=2017-02-13 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020214923/http://www.scotsman.com/news/politics/top-stories/chancellor-s-world-cup-fever-fails-to-grip-the-scots-1-681878 |archive-date=2012-10-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。比赛场地于2009年12月16日被公布，分别位于[[伦敦]]（3座）、[[曼彻斯特]]（2座）、[[伯明翰]]、[[布里斯托尔]]、[[利兹]]、[[利物浦]]、[[米尔顿凯恩斯]]、[[泰恩河畔纽卡斯尔]]、[[诺丁汉]]、[[普利茅斯]]、[[谢菲尔德]]和[[桑德兰]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/8414235.stm|title=Milton Keynes part of England's 2018 World Cup bid|work=BBC Sport |date=2009-12-06 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-14| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20091217032444/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/8414235.stm| archivedate= 2009-12-07| deadurl= no}}</ref>。

[[国际足联]]的官员们对英格兰的申办主张表示感兴趣。时任国际足联副主席戴维·威尔早在2004年5月就承诺为英格兰申办世界杯投上一票<ref name="will">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/go/click/rss/0.91/public/-/sport1/hi/football/3740851.stm| title=FIFA gives England hope |work=BBC News |place=London |date=2004-05-23 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en}}</ref>。2007年，曾带领[[德国]]成功申办[[2006年国际足联世界杯]]的[[弗朗茨·贝肯鲍尔]]在公开场合曾两次公开英格兰申办世界杯<ref>{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6307237.stm |title= Beckenbauer will back England bid |language= en |work= BBC Sport |location= London |date= 2007-01-28 |accessdate= 2018-08-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20081209004210/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6307237.stm |archive-date= 2008-12-09 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6921154.stm |title= England gets Beckenbauer backing |work=BBC Sport |date=2007-07-26 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en}}</ref>。时任国际足联主席[[塞普·布拉特]]称十分欢迎来自“足球故乡”的英格兰申办2018年世界杯<ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/4208814.stm| title=Blatter Welcomes England Cup Bid| work=BBC Sport| date=2005-09-02| accessdate=2018-08-14| language=en| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060423193810/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/4208814.stm| archive-date=2006-04-23| dead-url=no}}</ref>。布拉特在访问英格兰时与[[戴维·卡梅伦]]交谈了两次，卡梅伦表达出了对申办世界杯的支持，希望世界杯能够在英格兰举办<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/oct/06/digger-david-cameron-sepp-blatter |title=Prime minister to back 2018 World Cup bid in talks with Sepp Blatter |date=2007-10-23 |work=The Guardian |location=London |accessdate=2018-08-14 |first=Matt |last=Scott |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814170229/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/oct/06/digger-david-cameron-sepp-blatter |archive-date=2018-08-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年8月，在[[2010年国际足联世界杯]]上成功预测8场比赛结果的[[章鱼保罗]]回到英格兰，开始投身于英格兰的2018年世界杯申办活动<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://world.huanqiu.com/roll/2010-08/1035385.html |title=章鱼保罗投身2018世界杯 成英格兰申办形象大使 |publisher=环球网 |language=zh-hans |accessdate=2018-08-14 |date=2010-08-22 |author=中国广播网 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101101152151/http://world.huanqiu.com/roll/2010-08/1035385.html |archive-date=2010-11-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，2010年10月25日，章鱼保罗于奥伯豪森水族馆离世，享年2岁又8个月<ref>{{cite news |publisher=Mirror |date=2010-10-23 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |title=Paul the octopus, World Cup win-predicting psychic octopus, has died |language=en |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news-old/weird-world/2010/10/26/paul-the-octopus-world-cup-win-predicting-psychic-octopus-has-died-115875-22659455/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101229180016/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news-old/weird-world/2010/10/26/paul-the-octopus-world-cup-win-predicting-psychic-octopus-has-died-115875-22659455/ |archive-date=2010-12-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=章鱼保罗去世 德国水族馆"沉痛"拟为其立碑 |url=http://www.chinanews.com.cn/gj/2010/10-26/2614284.shtml |newspaper=中新网 |date=2010-10-25 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201055657/http://www.chinanews.com.cn/gj/2010/10-26/2614284.shtml |archive-date=2010-12-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.qq.com/a/20101026/001049.htm |title=章鱼保罗德国“仙逝” 世界杯8猜8中永成神迹 |date=2010-10-26 |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[腾讯新闻]] |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140119163052/http://sports.qq.com/a/20101026/001049.htm |archive-date=2014-01-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在申办2018年世界杯失败后，[[英格兰足球总会]]已经同意将展开关于申办[[2030年国际足联世界杯]]的调查工作<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.sohu.com/20180802/n545245573.shtml |title=足球真的要回家？英格兰准备申办2030世界杯！ |date=2018-08-02 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[搜狐|搜狐新闻]] }}</ref>。

已结束任期的英格兰足球总会主席特里斯曼爵士在2018年的一次采访中表示，在英格兰申办2018年国际足联世界杯的期间，他们的电脑曾遭到过来自黑客的攻击<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dongqiudi.com/archive/666023.html |title=前英足总主席：申办2018世界杯时，我们遭到了黑客攻击 |date=2018-05-23 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[懂球帝]] }}</ref>。

==== 葡萄牙和西班牙 ====
[[葡萄牙足球协会]]时任主席吉尔伯托·马代尔在2007年11月首次提出要与[[西班牙]]一同申办2018年国际足联世界杯<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.qq.com/a/20071129/000474.htm |title=葡萄牙希望和西班牙联合申办2018年世界杯 |author=[[新华网]] |language=zh-hans |accessdate=2018-08-14 |date=2007-11-29 |publisher=[[腾讯新闻]] }}</ref><ref name="telegraph20071127">{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/main.jhtml?view=DETAILS&grid=A1YourView&xml=/sport/2007/11/27/sfnwcp127.xml |last=Bond |first=David  |work=The Daily Telegraph  |place=London |date=2007-11-27 |title=Portugal and Spain to Launch Rival 2018 Bid  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080226173847/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/main.jhtml?view=DETAILS&grid=A1YourView&xml=%2Fsport%2F2007%2F11%2F27%2Fsfnwcp127.xml |archivedate=2008-02-26 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=485193&cc=3888 |title= Iberian threat to England's 2018 World Cup bid |work= ESPN |date=2007-11-27 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071201142734/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=485193&cc=3888| archivedate=2007-12-01 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。2008年2月18日，该申办意愿被时任国际足联主席[[塞普·布拉特]]确认<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.marca.com/edicion/marca/futbol/seleccion/es/desarrollo/1090960.html |title= España y Portugal se unen para pedir el Mundial de 2018 |language= es |last= Brotons |first= Pablo |work= [[马卡报]] |location= Madrid |date= 2008-02-18 |accessdate= 2018-08-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080514025206/http://www.marca.com/edicion/marca/futbol/seleccion/es/desarrollo/1090960.html |archive-date= 2008-05-14 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。然而，[[西班牙皇家足球协会]]时任主席安吉尔·玛利亚在2008年7月称西班牙只想以单个国家的名义申办世界杯，并不希望与葡萄牙合办<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.elpais.com/articulo/deportes/Villar/confirma/contactos/Lissavetzky/organizar/Mundial/2018/elpepudep/20080716elpepudep_10/Tes |title=Villar confirma contactos con Lissavetzky para organizar el Mundial 2018 |work= El País |location=Madrid |date= 2008-07-16 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=es}}</ref>。2008年11月23日，安吉尔·玛利亚在西班牙皇家足球协会主席重新选举后称，保证在他的新的任期内，基本目标就是把世界杯主办权带到西班牙，但他并未说明是以单个国家名义还是与葡萄牙合办<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/88/spain/2008/12/23/1026578/spain-portugal-confirm-2018-world-cup-bid|title=Spain-Portugal Confirm 2018 World Cup Bid|date=2010-12-23|work=Goal|accessdate=2018-08-14|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814170033/http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/88/spain/2008/12/23/1026578/spain-portugal-confirm-2018-world-cup-bid|archive-date=2018-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2008年12月23日，安吉尔·玛利亚发布声明，称他个人上认为西班牙应与葡萄牙一起共同举办世界杯<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2008/12/23/sports/SOC-WCup-Spain-Portugal-2018-Bid.php |title= Spain eyes joint 2018 World Cup bid with Portugal |language=en |work= International Herald Tribune |location= Paris  |date= 2008-12-23 |accessdate=2018-08-14 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204023957/http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2008/12/23/sports/SOC-WCup-Spain-Portugal-2018-Bid.php| archivedate= 2009-02-04 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。随后，在西班牙皇家足球协会高层会议后，西班牙和葡萄牙宣布了共同申办2018年世界杯的意向<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.marca.com/edicion/marca/futbol/seleccion/es/desarrollo/1194477.html |title=La RFEF concreta su candidatura conjunta al Mundial 2018 |work=[[马卡报]] |location=Madrid |date=2008-12-23 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=es<!--DASHBot--> |archive-url=https://archive.is/20081225231228/http://www.marca.com/edicion/marca/futbol/seleccion/es/desarrollo/1194477.html |archive-date=2008-12-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。西班牙体育报纸[[马卡报]]透露了更多的申办细节，如开幕式和决赛将分别在[[里斯本]]和[[马德里]]举行<ref>{{cite news |url= http://ultimahora.publico.clix.pt/noticia.aspx?id=1353757&idCanal=56 |location= Lisbon |title= Candidatura ibérica ao Mundial 2018 prevê abertura em Lisboa e final em Madrid |work= Público |date= 2008-12-20 |accessdate= 2018-08-14 |language= pt |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090205184203/http://ultimahora.publico.clix.pt/noticia.aspx?id=1353757&idCanal=56 |archivedate= 2009-02-05 |deadurl= yes }}</ref>。

西班牙球员[[塞斯克·法布雷加斯]]被任命为西班牙的世界杯申办大使<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.163.com/10/1009/14/6IIGAAHU00051CCL.html |title=小法助西班牙申办世界杯 亲承已100%康复盼上场 |date=2010-10-09 |publisher=[[网易|网易新闻]] |language=zh-hans |accessdate=2018-08-14 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://voice.hupu.com/hushi/soccer/5965.html |title=世界杯申办大使小法专访：梦想在家乡捧杯 |publisher=虎扑 |language=zh-hans |date=2010-10-07 |accessdate=2018-08-14 }}</ref>。西班牙球员[[劳尔·冈萨雷斯·布兰科]]和葡萄牙球员[[路易斯·菲戈]]被任命为西班牙与葡萄牙共同申办世界杯的形象大使<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.163.com/09/0519/09/59LTEQVI00051C8V.html |title=西葡联合申办2018世界杯 劳尔菲戈化身形象大使 |date=2009-05-19 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[网易|网易新闻]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090524081245/http://sports.163.com/09/0519/09/59LTEQVI00051C8V.html |archive-date=2009-05-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 俄罗斯 ====
早在2007年，就有传闻称俄罗斯将申办2018年国际足联世界杯<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/2007-10-16/16593229745.shtml |title=场内场外皆为对手 英俄争夺2018世界杯主办权 |author=东方体育日报 |publisher=[[新浪|新浪新闻]] |language=zh-hans |date=2007-10-16 |accessdate=2018-08-14 }}</ref>。然而，俄罗斯在2009年上半年才宣布申办2018年或2022年国际足联世界杯的意向，在最后一刻向[[国际足联]]提交了申办请求<ref>{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7838233.stm |title= Russia enters race to host 2018 |work= BBC Sport |date= 2009-01-20 |accessdate= 2018-08-14 |language= en |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180624060829/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7838233.stm |archive-date= 2018-06-24 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2009年10月9日，[[俄罗斯足球总会]]在[[莫斯科]]国营百货商店召开新闻发布会，宣布正式启动2018年或2022年国际足联世界杯的申办工作<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.163.com/09/1010/08/5L8IESFF000536VO.html |title=俄罗斯足协宣布正式启动世界杯申办工作 |author=[[新华网]] |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[网易|网易新闻]] |accessdate=2018-08-14 |date=2018-08-14 }}</ref>。俄罗斯时任总统[[普京]]对申办世界杯产生了浓厚的兴趣，并命令体育部长维塔利·穆特科开始准备申办工作。据维塔利·穆特科早些时候提交的一份报告，俄罗斯准备耗资101亿美元举办世界杯<ref>{{cite news | title = Putin orders sports minister to prepare bid for 2018 World Cup | url = http://en.rian.ru/sports/20090505/121448011.html | work = RIA Novosti | location = Moscow | date = 2009-05-05 | language = en | access-date = 2018-08-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013121938/http://en.rian.ru/sports/20090505/121448011.html | archive-date = 2012-10-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。俄罗斯世界杯申办委员会成员还包括俄罗斯足球联盟首席执行官阿列克谢·索洛金和亚力山大·达尔乔泽，担任申办计划总执行人和运营总监<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.russia2018-2022.com/en/the-bid/bid-committee.aspx |title= Bid committee |work= Russia 2018–2022 Bid |date = 2009-10 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20091012020705/http://www.russia2018-2022.com/en/the-bid/bid-committee.aspx| archivedate=2009-10-12 | deadurl= no}}</ref>。

共有14个城市被选为举办城市，分别为[[圣彼得堡]]、[[莫斯科]]、[[索契]]、[[叶卡捷琳堡]]、[[加里宁格勒]]、[[顿河畔罗斯托夫]]、[[克拉斯诺达尔]]、[[雅罗斯拉夫尔]]、[[下诺夫哥罗德]]、[[喀山]]、[[萨兰斯克]]、[[萨马拉]]和[[伏尔加格勒]]<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.russia2018-2022.com/en/the-bid/host-cities.aspx |title= Host cities |work= Russia 2018–2022 Bid |date = 2009-10 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |language=en| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20091023181459/http://www.russia2018-2022.com/en/the-bid/host-cities.aspx| archivedate=2009-10-23| deadurl= no}}</ref>。虽然在申办时俄罗斯境内并无超过8万坐席的体育场，但位于莫斯科的[[卢日尼基体育场]]已具备改造条件<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.rin.ru/eng/news///12466/7// |title=Russia ready to spend $10 bln on World Cup 2018 preparations |date=2009-04 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617103318/http://news.rin.ru/eng/news///12466/7// |archive-date=2018-06-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 2022年国际足联世界杯 ===
==== 澳大利亚 ====
2006年7月，[[堪培拉]]召开了一次澳大利亚政府首脑会议，在会上传出了澳大利亚将申办2018年国际足联世界杯的消息<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.163.com/06/0715/15/2M3625I600051C9U.html |title=澳大利亚申办2018世界杯 堪称中国足球最大敌人 |publisher=[[网易|网易体育]] |language=zh-hans |accessdate=2018-08-15 |date=2006-07-15 }}</ref>。一年后，即2007年9月，[[澳大利亚足球协会]]确认了申办2018年国际足联世界杯的消息<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.smh.com.au/news/football/socceroos-stars-coming-home-for-two-matches/2006/09/21/1158431837576.html |agency=AAP |title= Socceroos' stars coming home for two matches |work= Sydney Morning Herald |date=2007-09-21 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-14| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20071209231144/http://www.smh.com.au/news/football/socceroos-stars-coming-home-for-two-matches/2006/09/21/1158431837576.html| archivedate= 2007-12-09 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。先前，[[维多利亚州]]体育部长{{link-en|贾斯汀·马顿|Justin Madden}}于2006年5月称他希望他所在的州能够申办2018年世界杯<ref>{{cite news |url=http://keobongda247.com/world-cup-2018.html |work=Keobongda247 Sports VietNam |title=news aggregator world cup 2018 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713043040/http://keobongda247.com/world-cup-2018.html |archive-date=2018-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。时任澳大利亚足球协会主席{{link-en|弗兰克·洛伊|Frank Lowy}}于2008年2月称澳足协已考虑将16个体育场作为世界杯比赛场馆<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/story/0,22049,23259207-5006068,00.html |last=Smithies |first=Tom |language=en |title=Lowy's vision for soccer |date=2008-02-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205172915/http://www.news.com.au/dailytelegraph/story/0%2C22049%2C23259207-5006068%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-02-05
 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |work=The Daily Telegraph |place=Sydney }}</ref>。同月，前澳大利亚总理[[陆克文]]宣布[[澳大利亚政府]]将支持申办活动<ref>{{cite news |last=Gilmore |first=Heath |author2=Proszenko, Adrian |url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/football/pm-makes-the-perfect-pitch-for-world-cup/2008/02/23/1203467452577.html |language=en |title=PM makes the perfect pitch for World Cup |work=Sydney Morning Herald |date=2008-02-28 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184402/http://www.smh.com.au/news/football/pm-makes-the-perfect-pitch-for-world-cup/2008/02/23/1203467452577.html |archive-date=2016-03-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年12月，澳大利亚联邦体育部长{{link-en|凯特·艾丽斯|Kate Ellis}}宣布，澳大利亚政府将下拨4560万美元给澳大利亚足球协会以用来进行申办活动<ref>{{cite news |title=$45m for 2018 World Cup bid |url=http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,24778844-12377,00.html |agency=AAP |language=en |location=Sydney |date=2008-12-10 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206034706/http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,24778844-12377,00.html |archive-date=2009-02-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2009年7月，陆克文在[[苏黎世]]讨论了关于2018年世界杯申办的相关事项<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.australia2018-2022.com.au/news-updates_detail.aspx?view=8 |title=Australian Bid Page |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090720083535/http://www.australia2018-2022.com.au/news-updates_detail.aspx?view=8 |date=2009-07-20 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 |archive-date=2009-07-20}}</ref>。

在[[悉尼]]举办的2008年国际足联大会上，国际足联主席[[塞普·布拉特]]推荐澳大利亚将申办目标转向2022年世界杯<ref name="2022Bid">{{cite news |url=https://www.fifa.com/aboutfifa/federation/bodies/news/newsid=783630.html#joint+decision+2018+2022+fifa+world+cups |title=Joint decision on 2018 and 2022 FIFA World Cups |work=[[FIFA]] |date=2008-05-30 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080531132531/http://www.fifa.com/aboutfifa/federation/bodies/news/newsid%3D783630.html |language=en |archivedate=2008-05-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。但澳足协主席弗兰克·洛伊坚持称澳大利亚将申办2018年世界杯<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2008/06/21/2281753.htm?section=sport |agency=AFP |language=en |title= FFA to press on with 2018 Cup bid: Lowy |date= 21 June 2008 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |work= ABC News| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080623012033/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2008/06/21/2281753.htm?section=sport| archivedate= 2008-06-23<!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。然而，在2010年6月10日听取了[[亚足联]]主席关于2018年世界杯应该在欧洲举行的意见，澳大利亚最终退出了2018年世界杯的申办竞争，将目标转向2022年世界杯<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup-2010/teams/australia/7818364/World-Cup-2010-Australia-pull-out-of-World-Cup-2018-bidding.html |title= World Cup 2010: Australia pull out of World Cup 2018 bidding |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |date= 2010-06-10 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100613010525/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup-2010/teams/australia/7818364/World-Cup-2010-Australia-pull-out-of-World-Cup-2018-bidding.html| archivedate= 2010-06-10 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2010/jun/09/world-cup-2018-2022-europe |title=World Cup 2018 should be in Europe, says Asian Football Confederation |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=2010-06-10 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815091023/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2010/jun/09/world-cup-2018-2022-europe |archive-date=2018-08-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://worldcup.qq.com/a/20100611/001112.htm |title=澳大利亚退出2018世界杯申办 12年后或迎盛典 |date=2010-06-11 |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[腾讯新闻]] |accessdate=2018-08-15 }}</ref>。

澳大利亚最大的体育场在申办过程中被澳大利亚其他主要体育项目所使用，并且它们未来的比赛时间与世界杯可能会重叠。[[澳大利亚澳式足球联盟]]和[[全国橄榄球联赛]]声称，如果这些场馆因世界杯而被占用几个星期，会严重干扰到他们的赛季进程，影响他们赛事和俱乐部的生存能力<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/12/14/2770679.htm?site=sport&section=football |title=AFL concerns over world cup run deep. |date=2009-12-21 |work=ABC |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110430034758/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/12/14/2770679.htm?site=sport&section=football |archive-date=2011-04-30 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/sport/nrl/soccers-plan-to-displace-nrl/story-e6frexnr-1225808419104 |title=Soccer's plan to displace NRL |date=2009-12-21 |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=Sydney |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110501021425/http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/sport/nrl/soccers-plan-to-displace-nrl/story-e6frexnr-1225808419104 |archive-date=2011-05-01 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。特别是澳大利亚澳式足球联盟在此前宣城，在整个世界杯期间，墨尔本将不会放弃{{link-en|达克兰体育场|Docklands Stadium}}<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.smh.com.au/sport/football/cup-bid-needs-to-share-the-vision-20091212-kpim.html | work=The Sydney Morning Herald | title=Cup bid needs to share the vision | date=2009-12-13 | language=en | accessdate=2018-08-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701064838/http://www.smh.com.au/sport/football/cup-bid-needs-to-share-the-vision-20091212-kpim.html | archive-date=2014-07-01 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年5月9日，澳大利亚澳式足球联盟、全国橄榄球联赛和澳大利亚足球协会共同发布了一份声明，澳足协将保证澳大利亚澳式足球联盟和全国橄榄球联赛的赛季不被中断。如果申办成功，由于举办世界杯所造成的任何破坏，澳足协将积极赔偿损失<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.smh.com.au/sport/football/rival-codes-finally-shake-hands-on-deal-to-play-through-world-cup-20100509-uluq.html |title= Rival codes finally shake hands on deal to play through World Cup |first= Brad |last= Walter |date=2010-05-10 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 |work=The Sydney Morning Herald| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100512122253/http://www.smh.com.au/sport/football/rival-codes-finally-shake-hands-on-deal-to-play-through-world-cup-20100509-uluq.html| archivedate= 2010-05-12 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。随后，澳大利亚澳式足球联盟首席执行官{{link-en|安得烈·德米特里|Andrew Demetriou}}公开宣布支持申办世界杯，尽管他此前并不这样做<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theage.com.au/comment/not-every-afl-point-was-a-goal-20140303-3409o.html |title=Not every AFL point was a goal |publisher=The Age |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 |date=2014-03-03 |author=Tom Heenan |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306124308/http://www.theage.com.au/comment/not-every-afl-point-was-a-goal-20140303-3409o.html |archive-date=2014-03-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.heraldsun.com.au/ipad-application/world-cup-soccer-2020-decision/story-fn6bn88w-1225961153205 |title= World Cup soccer 2022 debate |first= Andrew |last= Demetriou |date= 2010-11-26 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |work=Herald Sun |location=Australia}}</ref>。[[弗朗茨·贝肯鲍尔]]推测，国际足联执行委员会其实并未考虑过澳大利亚澳式足球联盟、全国橄榄球联赛和澳大利亚足球协会之间的纠纷问题<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.heraldsun.com.au/ipad-application/argy-bargy-no-threat-to-world-cup-bid/story-fn6bn647-1225961988679 |title= Argy-bargy no threat to World Cup bid |first= David |last= Davutovic |date=2010-11-28 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en |work=Herald Sun |location=Australia}}</ref>。虽然最初澳大利亚似乎是主办权的热门竞争者，但最终澳大利亚仅获得了一票，弗朗茨·贝肯鲍尔表示十分吃惊<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2010-12-04/beckenbauer-astonished-by-australia-snub/2362520 |language=en |title=Beckenbauer astonished by Australia snub |date=2010-12-04 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309030443/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2010-12-04/beckenbauer-astonished-by-australia-snub/2362520 |archive-date=2014-03-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 日本 ====
当日本被曝出将要申办世界杯时，虽然日本曾与韩国合办过[[2002年国际足联世界杯]]，但他们还是被认为在这次世界杯申办过程中有着竞争关系<ref>{{cite news | title = The race to host World Cup 2018 and 2022 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7856716.stm#japan | work = BBC Sport | location = London | date = 2009-03-17 | language = en | accessdate = 2018-08-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140517122500/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/7856716.stm#japan | archive-date = 2014-05-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。虽然当时的日本并无8万坐席的体育场，但他们在申办[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]时就已提出过将建造一个多达10万坐席的体育场。日本同时承诺，如果日本获得了2022年世界杯的主办权，他们将开发一些的新转播技术，这意味着将允许为世界上400个体育场为3.6亿人提供实时的3D转播。比赛实况画面将被两百多个高清摄像机全方位捕捉，在各个球场的巨型屏幕上投射。此外，如果届时可以使用这种技术，日本将以全息格式转播世界杯。除了让全世界的观众在平面屏幕上观看3D成像，世界杯的全息投影将把比赛实况投射到体育场场地上，创造出一种更真实的情景。嵌入在播放表面下方的麦克风将记录所有声音，以增加现实感<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.popsci.com/technology/article/2010-05/world-cup-bid-japan-offers-project-live-3-d-holographic-games-pitches-worldwide |publisher=Popular Science |title=In 2022 World Cup Bid, Japan Offers to Broadcast Live, Full-Scale 3-D Holographic Games on Fields Worldwide |language=en |year=2010-05 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507211140/http://www.popsci.com/technology/article/2010-05/world-cup-bid-japan-offers-project-live-3-d-holographic-games-pitches-worldwide |archive-date=2017-05-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5gNVZsxBSbgXx268O16flQfqXOs_w |publisher=Agence France-Presse |title=Japan offers global 3-D telecasts in 2022 WC bid |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120129011023/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5gNVZsxBSbgXx268O16flQfqXOs_w |archive-date=2012-01-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.engadget.com/2010/05/20/japan-proposes-holographic-3d-broadcasts-for-2022-world-cup/ |publisher=Engadget |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 |date=2010-05-20 |title=Japan proposes holographic 3D broadcasts for 2022 World Cup |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205070204/http://www.engadget.com/2010/05/20/japan-proposes-holographic-3d-broadcasts-for-2022-world-cup/ |archive-date=2016-02-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年7月11日，在[[2010年国际足联世界杯]]上表现优异的日本前锋[[本田圭佑]]表示，他将全力帮助日本夺得2022年国际足联世界杯的主办权。日本世界杯申办委员会同日表示，本田圭佑将与前日本队主帅济科、特鲁西埃和奥西姆共同组成申办大使小组<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.163.com/10/0711/17/6BB2KA6J00014AEE.html |title=本田圭佑助日本申办2022年世界杯 |date=2010-07-11 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[网易|网易新闻]] |author=[[新华网]] }}</ref>。然而，在日本申办2016年奥运会失败后，[[日本足球协会]]副主席小仓纯二于2009年10月承认，日本主办2018年或2022年世界杯的机会变得越来越渺茫<ref>{{cite news| title = Japan World Cup bid rests on 2016 Olympic vote| first = Alastair | last = Himmer | url = https://www.reuters.com/article/olympicsNews/idUSSP35460420090123 | work = Reuters | date = 2009-01-22 | accessdate =2018-08-15 |language=en }}</ref>。2010年5月4日，在听取了[[亚足联]]主席关于2018年世界杯应该在欧洲举行的意见后，日本宣布将只申办2022年世界杯<ref name="Japan 2018 withdrawal">{{cite news | title = Japan drops bid to host 2018 World Cup to aim for 2022 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8659185.stm | work = BBC Sport | location = London | date = 2010-05-03 | accessdate = 2018-08-15 | language = en | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100507140239/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8659185.stm | archive-date = 2010-05-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==== 卡塔尔 ====
卡塔尔在申办之初就宣布只参与2022年世界杯的主办权竞争，试图成为第一个举办国际足联世界杯的[[阿拉伯国家]]<ref name="race20090317"/>。前[[卡塔尔埃米尔]]的儿子穆罕默德·阿勒萨尼被任命为申办委员会主席<ref>{{cite news |title=Qatar 2022 announces Bid Committee leadership |url=http://www.dubaichronicle.com/life/sport-life/qatar-2022-announces-bid-committee-leadership-7121 |work=Dubai Chronicle |date=2009-03-25 |deadurl=yes  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090602051207/http://www.dubaichronicle.com/life/sport-life/qatar-2022-announces-bid-committee-leadership-7121  |archivedate=2009-06-02 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 }}</ref>。卡塔尔原本计划以阿拉伯国家联合申办的方式进行竞争，并希望得到整个[[阿拉伯世界]]的支持，将其定位为弥合阿拉伯与西方世界之间的鸿沟的机会<ref>{{cite news |title = Qatar launch "unity" bid to stage 2022 World Cup finals | url = http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=647154&sec=worldcup2010&&cc=573 | work = ESPN | date = 2009-05-17| accessdate =2018-08-15 |language=en }}</ref>。2009年3月，穆罕默德·阿勒萨尼称卡塔尔已为主办2022年国际足联世界杯作好了准备<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://sports.163.com/09/0325/08/5584UO8600051C9U.html |title=卡塔尔已为承办2022年世界杯作好准备 |author=[[新华网]] |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[网易|网易新闻]] |accessdate=2018-08-15 |date=2009-03-25 }}</ref>。为成功申办2022年世界杯，卡塔尔于2009年11月在全国范围内展开了宣传活动<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rCt5n5iWTXU | title = Qatar 2022 FIFA World Cup Bid TV Commercial | date = 2009-11-15 | language = en | work = [[YouTube]] | accessdate = 2018-08-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170817052548/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rCt5n5iWTXU | archive-date = 2017-08-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

然而，外界对卡塔尔的申办提出了质疑，对其极端的高温表示了担忧<ref name=cool>{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/10093703.stm |title= Qatar pitches cool World Cup bid |first= Neil |last= Heathcote |work= BBC World News |date=2010-05-04 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100507215907/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/10093703.stm| archivedate=2010-05-07 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。以往的世界杯总是在六月和七月举行。在这期间，卡塔尔大部分地区的日间平均最高气温都超过了40°C，日均最低温度也超过了30°C<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.weather.com/outlook/travel/businesstraveler/wxclimatology/monthly/graph/QAXX0003?from=36hr_bottomnav_business |title=Monthly Averages for Doha, Qatar |work=The Weather Channel |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081229115428/http://www.weather.com/outlook/travel/businesstraveler/wxclimatology/monthly/graph/QAXX0003?from=36hr_bottomnav_business |archive-date=2008-12-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。对此，穆罕默德·阿勒萨尼回应说，如果这项赛事必须在六月或七月举办，卡塔尔将不得不借助新技术来对付炎热的天气。同时他还声明声明，卡塔尔已经开始了新技术的研发，准备建造一个可以控制温度的体育场<ref>{{cite news |title=Qatar will be great host for WC 2022 |first=Raajiv |last=Tripathi |author2=Nag, Arindam |url=http://www.qatar-tribune.com/data/20090325/content.asp?section=exclusive1_1 |work=Qatar Tribune |location=Doha |date=2009-05-25 |deadurl=yes  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090329073540/http://www.qatar-tribune.com/data/20090325/content.asp?section=exclusive1_1  |archivedate=2009-03-29 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15}}</ref>。最先拟议的五个体育场计划采用能降低体育场内温度达到20摄氏度的冷却技术。此外，在世界杯结束后，这些体育场馆的上层部分将在世界杯之后捐赠给体育基础设施较薄弱的国家<ref name=cool/>。

时任国际足联主席[[塞普·布拉特]]赞同了在[[中东地区]]举办世界杯的想法。他在2010年4月时说：“阿拉伯世界值得举办世界杯，该地区有22个国家，之前却从来没有机会来组织世界杯赛事”。同时，布拉特也称赞了卡塔尔的降温新技术，对外界向卡塔尔的质疑进行了反驳<ref>{{cite news |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/sport/2010/04/2010424184010305993.html |title=Blatter reaches out to Arabia |work=Al Jazeera |date=2010-04-25 |language=en |accessdate=2010-05-01 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100429041252/http://english.aljazeera.net/sport/2010/04/2010424184010305993.html| archivedate=2010-04-29 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。2010年7月28日，卡塔尔获得了巨大的鼓舞，时任[[亚足联]]主席[[默罕默德·本·哈曼]]在[[新加坡]]发表讲话时，本·哈曼明确表示他将为卡塔尔投出一票<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sportsfeatures.com/soccernews/story/47199/more-bad-news-for-australia-as-bin-hammam-talks-up-qatars-2022-bid.html |title=Bin Hammam talks up Qatar's 2022 bid |publisher=Sports Features Communications |date=2010-07-28 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101209222311/http://www.sportsfeatures.com/soccernews/story/47199/more-bad-news-for-australia-as-bin-hammam-talks-up-qatars-2022-bid.html |archivedate=2018-08-15 }}</ref>。

==== 韩国 ====
韩国宣布只申办2022年国际足联世界杯。2009年8月，前[[大韩民国外交部]]部长[[韩昇洲]]被任命为世界杯申办委员会主席<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.kfa.or.kr/eng_kfa/news/news/view.asp?g_conid=2009827162321&g_gubun=1 |title=Han Sung-Joo Appointed as the Chairman of the Bidding Committee |work=[[韩国足球协会]] |language=en |date=2009-08-20 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110427083109/http://www.kfa.or.kr/eng_kfa/news/news/view.asp?g_conid=2009827162321&g_gubun=1 |archivedate=2011-04-27 }}</ref>。同年9月，他在[[苏黎世]]与时任国际足联主席[[塞普·布拉特]]进行了会见。2010年1月，时任[[大韩民国总统]][[李明博]]在苏黎世的国际足联总部与布拉特进行了会见<ref>{{cite news |url=http://kr.news.yahoo.com/sports/npb/view?aid=20090926073606806i1 |script-title=ko:(인터뷰) 한승주 위원장 "국제 축구계, 2022 월드컵 유치 의사 환영 |date= 2009-09-26 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=ko |work= Yahoo! News Korea}}</ref>。

虽然韩国在申办之初并无8万坐席的体育场，但他们打算从现有的几个大型体育场中选取一个进行扩充升级，如[[首尔奥林匹克主竞技场]]、[[首尔世界杯竞技场]]、[[大邱体育场]]和[[仁川亚运主体育场]]<ref name="race20090317"/>。共有12个城市被韩国方面选为举办城市，分别为[[釜山广域市]]、[[天安市]]、[[大邱广域市]]、[[大田广域市]]、[[高阳市]]、[[光州广域市]]、[[仁川广域市]]、[[全州市]]、[[西归浦市]]、[[首尔特别市]]、[[水原市]]和[[蔚山广域市]]，其中仁川广域市和首尔特别市将有2个体育场作为举办场地<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.worldfootballinsider.com/Story.aspx?id=33064 |title=Korea 2022 Reveals Host Cities |publisher=World Football Insider |date=2010-03-04 |accessdate=2018-08-15 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100306150340/http://www.worldfootballinsider.com/Story.aspx?id=33064| archivedate= 2010-03-06 <!--DASHBot-->|language=en | deadurl= no}}</ref>。

==== 美国 ====
[[美国足球协会]]于2007年2月首次提出将申办国际足联世界杯，但当时的申办目标为2018年世界杯而非2022年世界杯<ref name=goff>{{cite news | url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/02/19/AR2007021900914.html | title=U.S. to Seek World Cup | work=The Washington Post | first=Steven | last=Goff | date=2007-02-20 | accessdate=2018-08-15 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815164257/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/02/19/AR2007021900914.html | archive-date=2018-08-15 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年1月28日，美国足球协会宣布将同时申办2018年和2022年世界杯<ref name="USA 2018and2022">{{cite news |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=614052&sec=world&cc=5901 |title=U.S. to bid for 2018 and 2022 World Cups |agency= Associated Press |work=ESPNsoccernet |location=Chicago |date=2009-01-29 | accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090131230810/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story?id=614052&sec=world&cc=5901| archivedate= 2009-01-31 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。{{link-en|Univision媒体集团|Univision}}董事长戴维·唐斯被任命为世界杯申办委员会的领导人<ref>{{cite news |url= http://voices.washingtonpost.com/soccerinsider/2009/02/usa_in_18_or_22.html |title= USA in '18 (or '22) |first= Steve |last= Goff |work= The Washington Post |date= 2009-02-02 |accessdate= 2018-08-15 |language= en |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183320/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/soccerinsider/2009/02/usa_in_18_or_22.html |archive-date= 2016-03-03 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。时任国际足联副主席兼[[中北美洲及加勒比海足球协会]]主席{{link-en|杰克·华纳 (足球高管)|Jack Warner (football executive)|杰克·华纳}}于2007年8月称，他将尽最大可能将世界杯主办权带到中北美洲及加勒比海地区<ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6939170.stm| title=Caborn hits back at Warner attack| work=BBC Sport| date=2007-08-10| language=en| accessdate=2007-10-28| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080113042625/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6939170.stm| archive-date=2008-01-13| dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，华纳同时也建议美国足球协会将申办视线全部转移至2022年世界杯上<ref>{{cite news| url=http://msn.foxsports.com/soccer/story/8204792/Warner-wants-U.S.-to-bid-for-2022-World-Cup| title=Warner wants U.S. to bid for 2022 World Cup| work=Fox Sports| accessdate=2008-06-04| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080606193657/http://msn.foxsports.com/soccer/story/8204792/Warner-wants-U.S.-to-bid-for-2022-World-Cup| archivedate=2008-06-06| deadurl=yes| language=en}}</ref>。

2009年4月，申办委员会在美国境内初步确定了70个体育场作为比赛场地<ref name="70 stadiums">{{cite news | title=2018 OR 2022 FIFA World Cup Bid Committee Contacts 70 US Venues | date=2009-04-08 | url=http://soccer.teamusa.org/news/2009/04/08/2018-or-2022-fifa-world-cup-bid-committee-contacts-70-us-venues/11583 | work=USA Soccer | accessdate=2018-08-15 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315171124/http://soccer.teamusa.org/news/2009/04/08/2018-or-2022-fifa-world-cup-bid-committee-contacts-70-us-venues/11583 | archive-date=2012-03-15 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |url=https://www.sportskeeda.com/football/fifa-world-cup-2018-guide-to-the-12-host-stadiums |title=FIFA World Cup 2018: Guide to the 12 host stadiums |date=2018-01-20 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |publisher=Sportskeeda |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630105711/https://www.sportskeeda.com/football/fifa-world-cup-2018-guide-to-the-12-host-stadiums |archive-date=2018-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。经过两个月的初步筛查，场馆数量被削减到45个<ref name="45 stadiums">{{Cite press release |title=USA Bid Committee Issues Requests For Proposals to 37 Potential FIFA World Cup Host Cities For 2018 or 2022 |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/articles/viewArticle.jsp_14876672.html  |publisher=United States Soccer Federation  |date=2009-06-16  |accessdate=2018-08-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090619071040/http://www.ussoccer.com/articles/viewArticle.jsp_14876672.html  |archivedate=2009-06-19  |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。随后，在2009年8月场馆数目又被削减至32个<ref name="32 stadiums">{{cite press release |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Federation-Services/2009/08/27-Cities-Chosen-For-World-Cup-Bid.aspx |title=USA Bid Committee Announces List of 27 Cities Still in Contention For Inclusion in U.S. Bid to Host FIFA World Cup in 2018 or 2022 |date=2009-08-20 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |publisher=United States Soccer Federation |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090926202259/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Federation-Services/2009/08/27-Cities-Chosen-For-World-Cup-Bid.aspx |archivedate=2009-09-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2010年1月，附有21个场馆的最终名单出炉。举办城市分别为[[亚特兰大]]、[[巴尔的摩]]、[[波士顿]]、[[达拉斯]]、[[丹佛]]、[[休斯敦]]、[[印第安纳波利斯]]、[[堪萨斯城 (密苏里州)|堪萨斯城]]、[[洛杉矶]]、[[迈阿密]]、[[纳什维尔]]、[[纽约]]、[[费城]]、[[菲尼克斯 (亚利桑那州)|菲尼克斯]]、[[聖地牙哥 (加利福尼亞州)|圣地亚哥]]、[[西雅图]]、[[坦帕 (佛罗里达州)|坦帕]]和[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]。其中，洛杉矶、西雅图、达拉斯和华盛顿哥伦比亚特区拥有多个达标的场馆。这21个场馆的平均座位数量为77000个，其中有7个体育场至少有80000个座席，并且没有任何一个场馆的座位数少于65000个<ref name="18 cities chosen">{{cite press release |url=http://www.gousabid.com/news/entry/bid-committee-announces-official-bid-cities/ |title=Bid Committee announces official bid cities |date=2010-01-12 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en |publisher=The USA Bid Committee }}{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

