== 反应 ==
为了庆祝卡塔尔获得[[2022年国际足联世界杯]]的主办权，[[多哈]]街头举行了庆祝活动<ref>[[Al Jazeera English]]. 2010-12-02. 18:00 GMT.</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9252710.stm|title=A World Cup miracle |date=2010-12-02 |work=BBC Sport |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20101203045716/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9252710.stm| archivedate= 2010-12-03<!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。{{link-en|卡塔尔交易所|Qatar Exchange}}在卡塔尔获选后的交易量暴涨<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-12/qatar-shares-head-for-2-year-high-on-growth-prospects-linked-to-world-cup.html | work=Bloomberg | first1=Zahra | last1=Hankir | first2=Ahmed | last2=Namatalla | title=Egypt Shares Gain on View Central Bank May Cut Interest Rates, Led by CIBE | date=2010-12-12 | language=en | accessdate=2018-08-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104150318/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-12/qatar-shares-head-for-2-year-high-on-growth-prospects-linked-to-world-cup.html | archive-date=2012-11-04 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。时任[[伊朗]]总统[[马哈茂德·艾哈迈迪内贾德]]向卡塔尔表示了祝贺，认为主办这次世界杯可以促进[[波斯湾]]地区和[[中东]]地区的足球运动。他还说，伊朗准备帮助卡塔尔举办这项赛事。他同时强调了区域国家间合作利用体育资源和机会的必要性<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/ty/2013/11-11/5485845.shtml |author=京华时报 |title=伊朗希望协办世界杯 决定权仍握在卡塔尔手里 |publisher=[[中国新闻网]] |language=zh-hans |date=2013-11-11 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112010815/http://www.chinanews.com/ty/2013/11-11/5485845.shtml |archive-date=2013-11-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 贿选指控 ===
这次投票结果在失利的国家中也有强烈反响。大多数英国报纸声称2018年世界杯是“卖给”俄罗斯的，同时来自西班牙、荷兰和日本等国家的媒体就俄罗斯和卡塔尔的经济实力提出了质疑。美国报纸《[[西雅图时报]]》和《[[华尔街日报]]》称这次世界杯主办国投票环节中充满了勾结和腐败<ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/9253692.stm |work=BBC News | title=English media angry at Fifa 'fix' | date=2010-12-03 |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15}}</ref>。

[[拜仁慕尼黑股份公司]]监事会主席[[乌利·赫内斯]]称国际足联主席塞普·布拉特对世界杯主办国投票失去了控制，并称国际足联内部存在着大量丑闻，一桩丑闻与另一桩丑闻接踵而至<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/861377/afc-chief-raises-prospect-of-blatter-challenge?cc=4716 |title=AFC Chief Raises Prospect of Blatter Challenge |publisher=[[ESPN]] |language=en |accessdate=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110427082947/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/861377/afc-chief-raises-prospect-of-blatter-challenge?cc=4716 |archive-date=2011-04-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年5月10日，英国世界杯申办委员会主席{{link-en|戴维·特里斯曼|David Triesman}}对一个[[专责委员会 (英国)|专责委员会]]透露称有4个国际足联委员会成员向他索取各种各样的东西来换取选票<ref>{{cite news |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/917869/lord-triesman-accuses-four-fifa-officials-of-impropriety |work=[[ESPN]] |title=Triesman accuses four FIFA members |date=2011-05-10 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024215913/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/917869/lord-triesman-accuses-four-fifa-officials-of-impropriety |archive-date=2012-10-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同日，《星期日泰晤士报》报道，两位国际足联委员会成员{{link-en|伊萨·哈耶托|Issa Hayatou}}和{{link-en|贾可·阿努马|Jacques Anouma}}获得了150万美元以换取赞成卡塔尔的选票<ref>{{cite news |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/918397/fifa-demands-evidence-of-corruption- |work=ESPN Soccernet |title=FIFA demands evidence of corruption |date=2011-05-11 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024224254/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/918397/fifa-demands-evidence-of-corruption- |archive-date=2012-10-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同月30日，[[国际足联]]主席[[塞普·布拉特]]在一次新闻发布会上反驳了《星期日泰晤士报》的说法，而在当天被停职的{{link-en|杰克·华纳 (足球高管)|Jack Warner (football executive)|杰克·华纳}}在调查中泄露了国际足联总书记杰里奥·瓦尔克的电子邮件，这表明卡塔尔已经“购买”了2022年世界杯的主办权。瓦尔克随后发表了一份声明，否认他曾暗示这是贿赂，而是说该国“利用其财政实力游说支持”。同时，卡塔尔官员否认有任何不当行为<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.reuters.com/article/2011/05/30/us-soccer-fifa-qatar-idUSTRE74T4J420110530 |title= Qataris brush off allegations of buying World Cup rights |agency= [[Reuters]] |first= Regan E. |last= Doherty |date= 2011-05-30 |accessdate= 2018-08-15 |language= en |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151015225134/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/05/30/us-soccer-fifa-qatar-idUSTRE74T4J420110530 |archive-date= 2015-10-15 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。同年11月，[[BBC]]播放了一名为{{link-en|国际足联的肮脏秘密|FIFA's Dirty Secrets}}的纪录片，片中称国际足联官员在1989至1999年间收到了巨额贿赂，但国际足联没有对此进行调查<ref>BBC One ''Panorama'', 2010-11-29.</ref><ref name="Defend">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-11874091 |title=BBC defends Panorama investigation into FIFA 'bribes' |work=[[BBC News]] |publisher=[[BBC|British Broadcasting Corporation]] |date=2010-11-30 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141120194929/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-11874091 |archive-date=2014-11-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-11866165 |title=Profiles:Fifa accused |work=BBC News |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2010-11-29 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408172157/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-11866165 |archive-date=2015-04-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，德国足球协会主席{{link-en|西奥·茨旺齐格|Theo Zwanziger}}也曾要求过国际足联对卡塔尔获选主办权一事展开调查<ref>{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13613314.stm |title= German Federation asks Fifa for inquiry into Qatar 2022 |work=[[BBC|BBC Sport]] |date= 2011-06-01 |accessdate=2018-08-15 |language=en | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110601111502/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13613314.stm| archivedate=2011-06-01 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref>。

